{"id": "art-194", "label": "Art. 194", "title": "Art. 194", "slug": "art-194", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 194 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Adunarea general&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> are urm&#259;toarele <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span>\nprincipale:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)s&#259;\naprobe <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> financiar&#259; anual&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; stabileasc&#259; repartizarea profitului\nnet;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_816747499\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1965\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_816747499\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)s&#259; desemneze administratorii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncenzorii, s&#259; îi revoce/demit&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ns&#259; le dea desc&#259;rcare de activitate, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ns&#259; decid&#259; contractarea auditului financiar, atunci când acesta nu are\ncaracter obligatoriu, potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_956277066\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1964\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_956277066\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)s&#259; decid&#259; urm&#259;rirea administratorilor <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cenzorilor pentru daunele pricinuite <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, desemnând <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npersoana îns&#259;rcinat&#259; s&#259; o exercite;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)s&#259;\nmodifice actul constitutiv.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)În acest din urm&#259; caz,\ndac&#259; în actul constitutiv se prevede dreptul de retragere a asociatului\npentru c&#259; nu este de acord cu modific&#259;rile aduse acestuia, se\naplic&#259; <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>224</span><span style='color:black'> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n</span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>225</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>"}